Post: Due to local government guidelines to manage the COVID-19 health emergency across the country, our business centers in Iloilo and Tacloban are temporarily close...d until further notice. In addition, our Davao business centers will also cease operations effective Thursday, March 26. Offices in Luzon will remain closed. Our live customer service will not be available until further notice. Customers may reach out to their financial advisors for any concern on their policies. Alternatively, customers may review and manage their policies through customer portal PRUAccess at https://pruaccess.prulifeuk.com.ph/ or email PRU Customer Action Team at contact.us@prulifeuk.com.ph. We continue to assess and release more timely announcements as the local authorities implement further measures and guidelines.
